#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the documentation for the &systemsettings; module that configures "
"mice and other pointing devices."
msgstr ""
"To je dokumentacija za modul &systemsettings;, ki konfigurira miške in druge "
"kazalne naprave."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid "Systemsettings"
msgstr "Sistemske nastavitve"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "mouse"
msgstr "miška"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This module allows you to configure your pointing device. Your pointing "
"device may be a mouse, a trackball, a touchpad, or another piece of hardware "
"that performs a similar function."
msgstr ""
"Ta modul vam omogoča nastavitev vaše kazalne naprave. Ta je lahko miška, "
"sledilna kroglica, sledilna ploščica ali pa kakšen drug kos strojne opreme, "
"ki opravlja podobno funkcijo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "General"
msgstr "Splošno"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "Left handed mouse"
msgstr "Levoročna miška"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are left-handed, you may prefer to swap the functions of the "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> and <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> buttons "
"on your pointing device by checking this option. If your pointing device has "
"more than two buttons, only those that function as the <mousebutton>left</"
"mousebutton> and <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> buttons are affected. For "
"example, if you have a three-button mouse, the <mousebutton>middle</"
"mousebutton> button is unaffected."
msgstr ""
"Če ste levičar, boste morda raje zamenjali funkciji gumbov "
"<mousebutton>levega</mousebutton> in <mousebutton>desnega</mousebutton> "
"klika na svoji kazalni napravi tako, da potrdite to možnost. Če ima vaša "
"kazalna naprava več kot dva gumba, to vpliva samo na gumba, ki delujeta kot "
"gumba <mousebutton>levi</mousebutton> in <mousebutton>desni</mousebutton>. "
"Če imate na primer miško s tremi gumbi, to ne vpliva na <mousebutton>srednji "
"gumb</mousebutton>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Press left and right buttons for middle-click"
msgstr "Pritisnite levi in desni gumb za srednji klik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this item if you don't have a &MMB;. You can press the left and right "
"mouse buttons at the same time to emulate middle-click."
msgstr ""
"Označite to potrditveno polje, če nimate &MMB;. S hkratnim pritiskom levega "
"in desnega miškinega gumba lahko posnemate srednji klik."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pointer speed"
msgstr "Hitrost kazalca"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option allows you to change the relationship between the distance that "
"the mouse pointer moves on the screen and the relative movement of the "
"physical device itself (which may be a mouse, trackball, or some other "
"pointing device.)"
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost vam omogoča spreminjanje razmerja med razdaljo premika kazalca po "
"zaslonu in relativnim pomikanjem same fizične naprave (ki je lahko miška, "
"sledilna kroglica ali kakšna druga kazalna naprava.)"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pointer acceleration"
msgstr "Pospešitev kazalke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Standard</guilabel> mode adjusts the amount of pointer "
"acceleration according to how fast you move the mouse. If you set it to "
"<guilabel>None</guilabel>, the acceleration remains constant regardless of "
"speed."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Standardni</guilabel> način prilagodi količino pospeševanja "
"kazalca glede na to, kako hitro premikate miško. Če ga nastavite na "
"<guilabel>Brez</guilabel>, ostane pospešek konstanten ne glede na hitrost."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrolling: Invert scroll direction"
msgstr "Drsno pomikanje: Obrnite smer pomikanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With this check box selected, the scroll wheel (if any) will work in the "
"opposite direction (so that if rolling the top of the scroll wheel towards "
"you previously causes a scroll down, then it will now cause a scroll up)."
msgstr ""
"Ko je izbrano to potrditveno polje, bo drsno kolesce (če obstaja) delovalo v "
"nasprotni smeri (tako da če je premikanje vrha drsnega kolesca proti vam "
"prej povzročilo drsenje navzdol, bo zdaj povzročilo drsenje navzgor)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In &plasma; 5.13 you find the setting to use single or double mouse clicks "
"to open files and folders in the module <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/"
"workspaceoptions/index.html\">Workspace</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"V &plasma; 5.13 najdete nastavitev za uporabo enojnih ali dvojnih klikov "
"miške za odpiranje datotek in map v modulu <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/"
"workspaceoptions/index.html\">Delovni prostor</ulink>."

#~ msgid "Acceleration profile"
#~ msgstr "Profil pospeševanja"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The <guilabel>Adaptive</guilabel> profile is the default profile for all "
#~ "devices and takes the current speed of the device into account when "
#~ "deciding on acceleration. The <guilabel>Flat</guilabel> profile is simply "
#~ "a constant factor applied to all device deltas, regardless of the speed "
#~ "of motion."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Profil <guilabel>Prilagodljiv</guilabel> je privzeti profil za vse "
#~ "naprave in pri odločanju o pospeševanju upošteva trenutno hitrost "
#~ "naprave. Profil <guilabel>Konstanten</guilabel> je preprosto konstanten "
#~ "faktor, ki se uporablja za vse delte naprave ne glede na hitrost gibanja."

#, fuzzy
#~ msgid ""
#~ "This module is divided into two tabs: <link linkend=\"mouse-general"
#~ "\">General</link> and <link linkend=\"mouse-advanced\">Advanced</link>."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ta modul je razdeljen na 2 jezička: <link linkend=\"mouse-general"
#~ "\">Splošno</link> in <link linkend=\"mouse-general\">Napredno</link>"

#~ msgid "Advanced"
#~ msgstr "Napredno"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "A high value for the acceleration multiplier will lead to large movements "
#~ "of the mouse pointer on the screen, even when you only make a small "
#~ "movement with the physical device."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Velika vrednost za mnogokratnik pospeševanja bo povzročila velike premike "
#~ "kazalca na zaslonu, četudi bodo premiki fizične naprave le majhni."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "A multiplier between <guilabel>1x</guilabel> and <guilabel>3x</guilabel> "
#~ "will works well for many systems. With a multiplier over <guilabel>3x</"
#~ "guilabel> the mouse pointer may become difficult to control."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Mnogokratnik med <guilabel>1x</guilabel> in <guilabel>3x</guilabel> je "
#~ "ustrezen na večini sistemov. Z vrednostjo preko <guilabel>3x</guilabel> "
#~ "bo miškin kazalec morda težko nadzorovati."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The threshold is the smallest distance that the mouse pointer must move "
#~ "on the screen before acceleration has any effect. If the movement is "
#~ "within the threshold, the mouse pointer moves as if the acceleration were "
#~ "set to <guilabel>1x</guilabel>."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Meja vleke je najmanjša razdalja, za katero se mora na zaslonu premakniti "
#~ "kazalec, preden učinkuje pospeševanje. Če je premik znotraj meje, se "
#~ "kazalec giblje kot da bi bil njegov pospešek nastavljen na <guilabel>1x</"
#~ "guilabel>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Thus, when you make small movements with the physical device (&eg; "
#~ "mouse), you still have fine control of the mouse pointer on the screen, "
#~ "whereas larger movements of the physical device will move the mouse "
#~ "pointer rapidly to different areas on the screen."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Tako imate, kadar premikate fizično napravo (&npr; miško), še vedno dober "
#~ "nadzor nad kazalcem na zaslonu medtem, ko večji premiki fizične naprave "
#~ "kazalec hitro premaknejo na druga območja zaslona."

#, fuzzy
#~| msgid ""
#~| "You can set the threshold value by dragging the slider button or by "
#~| "clicking the up/down arrows on the spin-button to the left of the slider."
#~ msgid ""
#~ "You can set the threshold by entering a value into the edit box or by "
#~ "clicking the up/down arrows to the right of the box."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Vrednost meje lahko nastavite z vlečenjem drsnika ali klikom na puščici "
